In one perl file may be one or more packages, but 
outline does not show packages - only modules and 
subroutines.

Example:

\#==========================

package Package::Module1;

sub \_init 
\{
\# ...
\}

package Package::Module2;

sub \_init 
\{
\# ...
\}

1;

\#==========================

